{"tid":2233872,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[民主黨My香港] 白鴿又含政府做朝廷鷹犬","createTime":"2020-10-07T12:40:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-31T07:40:18.000Z","uid":84668,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0f8d54caf72643f207a6c14c01fc4b6f5cb959a0","tid":2233872,"uid":84668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:40:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=825227291613557&amp;id=100023788811850\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D825227291613557%26id%3D100023788811850&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmWjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=9e9385a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=825227291613557&amp;id=100023788811850</a><br />\n<br />\n黃大仙區議會全體議員都係民主派<br />\n俾手足叫金大仙就係人都知<br />\n但原來老鴿都係會抽你後腿幫政府維穩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n難得有新血年青區議員提倡改革<br />\n而老牌區議員譚香文都支持新血既建議<br />\n<br />\n白鴿亦都扮晒蟹交足戲表情扭曲<br />\n講撚到大義凜然為民請命咁<br />\n<br />\n以為黃大仙區議會全黃<br />\n今次夾政府改革實食冇痴牙啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢老味<br />\n結果白鴿竟然繼續含政府投讚成票支持政府決定<br />\n繼續剝削基層巿民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幫政府維穩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n根本民主黨就係建制B隊<br />\n<br />\n老鴿一日未除<br />\n香港一日都冇改變<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0b06977468a1464ab01d6048c5d5b9d296596ce","tid":2233872,"uid":84668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T12:43:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"114de9bb2c80901c994759a811c55e05d9d62009","tid":2233872,"uid":8466